-- MOVES-Christian Menegatti joins Windhaven Investment from Roubini Global
-- 
-- Tue Oct 14, 2014 02:41PM EDT
-- None



Oct 14 (Reuters) - Boston-based Windhaven Investment Management Inc, a subsidiary of Charles Schwab Corp <SCHW.N>, said it had appointed Christian Menegatti chief investment strategist.

Menegatti joins from Roubini Global Economics, where he was managing director and global head of research, Windhaven said in a statement.